  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China once again hosted its largest wind power expo, <A href="http://www.chinawind.org.cn/home.html">China Wind 2011</a>, surpassing <A href="../blog-posts/two-international-conferences-china-highlight-importance-wind-energy">last year‚Äôs exhibition</a> with the number of companies and the exhibition floor space increasing by 50%.  Not surprisingly for an event in Beijing, the China market continued to be a major focus, but this year there was much more sense of a global market with increasing interest in new emerging markets, in particular Latin America.</p></div>
