  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/senate-energy-committee-questions-department-energy-secretary-chu-us-energy-spending-and-">Senate Energy Committee Questions Department of Energy Secretary Chu on U.S. Energy Spending and Clean Energy Competitiveness With China</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/ChuTestimonyFeb2011.jpg" alt="" title="" width="165" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
